data.description: Village Cape Cod design 3 bedroom 1 1/2 bath home. Features include kitchen with dining area, spacious living room, 2 main level and one upper level bedrooms, full bath on the main level is made for handicapped accessibility with walk-in shower, roll under sink area, home has most windows replaced with vinyl replacement windows, recently updated roof, furnace, ample storage space in the lower level for rec room, and workshop and storage, home exterior has handicapped accessible ramp, nicely landscaped yard with 2 car detached garage, natural gas forced air heat with central air!
